Rxvt-unicode, known as urxvt is fast and lightweight terminal emulator.

== Install ==
{{emerge|x11-terms/rxvt-unicode}}

== Font ==
{{file|~/.Xresources||<pre>
URxvt.font:               xft:Terminus:antialias=false:pixelsize=9
</pre>}}

== Scrollbar ==
{{file|~/.Xresources||<pre>
URxvt.scrollBar:          false
</pre>}}

== Url handling ==
{{file|~/.Xresources||<pre>
URxvt.perl-ext-common:  default,matcher
URxvt.urlLauncher:      /usr/bin/uzbl-browser
URxvt.matcher.button:   1
</pre>}}

== Icons ==
=== Menu icon ===
This adds menu entry and menu icon for urxvt.
If urxvt doesnt have a .desktop file, create one.
{{file|/usr/share/applications/urxvt.desktop||<pre>
[Desktop Entry]
Name=Urxvt
Comment=Terminal emulator
TryExec=urxvt
Exec=urxvt
Icon=terminal
Type=Application
Categories=GNOME;GTK;Utility;TerminalEmulator;System;
StartupNotify=true
</pre>}}

=== Application icon ===
For setting application icon urxvt has to be compiled with afterimage USE flag.
{{file|~/.Xresources||<pre>
URxvt.iconFile:    /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/Terminal.svg
</pre>}}

